msgid ""
msgstr "Abuse about name"

#. HTML: </h5><p>
#. REF: sc22, ms2V_50
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:2.2.9"
msgid "Upasampanno upasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo hīnena hīnaṃ vadeti, avakaṇṇakaṃ javakaṇṇakaṃ dhaniṭṭhakaṃ saviṭṭhakaṃ kulavaḍḍhakaṃ—"
