msgid "“oṭṭhosi, meṇḍosi, goṇosi, gadrabhosi, tiracchānagatosi, nerayikosi, natthi tuyhaṃ sugati, duggatiyeva tuyhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, vācāya pācittiyassa."
