msgstr "If one who is fully ordained, wishing to revile, wishing to insult, wishing to humiliate another who is fully ordained, says what is high to one who is low—a camel/a ram/an ox/a donkey/an animal/one bound for hell—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:2.2.78"
msgid "“paṇḍitosi, byattosi, medhāvīsi, bahussutosi, dhammakathikosi, natthi tuyhaṃ duggati, sugatiyeva tuyhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, vācāya pācittiyassa."
